briefTitle: Safety, Efficacy, and Pharmacokinetic Behavior of Leuprolide Mesylate in Subjects With Advanced Prostate Carcinoma
officialTitle: An Open-Labeled, Singled-Arm Study of the Safety, Efficacy, and Pharmacokinetic Behavior of Leuprolide Mesylate for Injectable Suspension (LMIS 50 mg) in Subjects With Advanced Prostate Carcinoma
summary: The study will evaluate if Leuprolide Mesylate is safe and effective in the treatment of subjects with advanced prostate carcinoma, when administered as two injections six months apart.

primaryOutcome.timeFrame: baseline to 28 days, 28 days to 336 days
